Now, I have to take my hat off to all the high level bards.  Its damn hard trying to keep 3 songs going at once.  Hehe, I have been playing a bard alt lately and I suck at twisting.  I can get two down pat, but I cant seem to be able to consistently twist three songs.  I admire bards like Kestri, she makes it look easy.  I love playing the bard (mine is lv25 currently) over playing a warrior (which I have a lv39 warrior).  I guess its because I need to be able to mezz things!  =)<br>
