Now, I do not agree that bards are limited.  How many times have raids gone looking for a bard for their resist songs, mana songs, heal songs, speed songs, etc.  Bards cant tank, true, but they can deal damage.  Where does it state that they NEED to be able to tank?  I would think if the party has a decent tank and the bard is controlling his aggro, he can step in and add to the damage dealt.<br>
<br>
Bards = every other class in EQ.  They all have their situations where they are needed or not. <p><DIV ALIGN="center">
