<br>
The reason bards are not as respected as they should be is because of the difficulty it takes to play an amazing bard.  Being aware of that difficulty, and being aware of how many idiots try to play it, you end up with a very hard class represented by a lot of dumbarses and that results in a lack of respect for the class.<br>
<br>
Bards are only meant to be played by people with 4 arms, 4 eyes, and 2 brains.  If you don't got that, then I suggest you stay away from the class and let the real bards shine through. <p><br>
